QuestData.Title: The Warchief Beckons
QuestData.Description: Greetings, $p. I am here on behalf of Lady Sylvanas Windrunner. I should hope you recognize the name.$B$B<Nathanos thrusts a sealed envelope into your hand.>$B$BRead it and follow me.$B$BYou can read, can't you?
QuestData.LogDescription: Read the Royal Summons and follow Nathanos Blightcaller through the portal to Durotar.

Objectives.Objective: Report to the Dark Lady's Fleet
